<style>
    
    .header-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }


   
    #save-btn,
    #cancel-btn {
        display: none;
    }

    #loading-indicator {
        display: none;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    #smsContent-input {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        min-height: 300px;
        max-height: 100%;
        resize: vertical;
        padding: 0.5rem;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .close-btn {
        float: right;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
</style>

<div id="sms-content-container">
    <div class="header-row">
        <h2>SMS Content Settings</h2>
        <div>
            <button id="edit-btn" class="btn btn-primary">Edit</button>
            <button id="save-btn" class="btn btn-primary">Save</button>
            <button id="cancel-btn" class="btn btn-danger">Cancel</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="loading-indicator">
        <div>Loading...</div>
    </div>

    <label for="smsContent-input">SMS Content:</label>
    <textarea id="smsContent-input" disabled>
Subject: Order Confirmation – Thank You for Your Order!

Dear [Client's Name],

Thank you for your order with [Your Photo Lab Name]. We're pleased to let you know that we've received your request and have started processing it.

We truly appreciate your trust in our services and look forward to delivering high-quality results for you. If we need any additional details, we will contact you shortly.

Should you have any questions or specific instructions regarding your order, feel free to reply to this email.

Thank you once again!

Best regards,

[Your Full Name]
[Your Position, e.g., Studio Manager]
[Your Photo Lab Name]
[Phone Number] | [Email Address] | [Website or Social Media if any]
    </textarea>
</div>

<script src="~/js/smsSettings.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
